						               													<description>Gormiti (The Invincible Lords of Nature) is a collectible mineatures game with a very big board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player chooses a team of creatures with every creature having a number under their left foot, and a corresponding card with their (single) stats.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The gameboard is divided into squares, and the game consists of moving the creatures and attacking the opponents creatures.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;An attack is played out with the attacker moving a monster up to the number under the foot, and then adding the remainder to the number on the creatures card; if this number is larger than the defenders number on foot plus card value, then the attacker wins, else the defender does. The loosing creature is removed from the board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is the player with the last surviving monsters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
